  "hashAlgorithm": "blake2b-256",
  "body": {
    "summary": "We consider this governance action to be constitutional.",
    "rationaleStatement": "This proposal is an Info Action documenting the framework of the ecosystem budget process operated by Intersect. Under the Cardano Constitution, an Info Action is defined as an action having no effect beyond on-chain recording, and this proposal remains within that scope. It meets the formal requirements for a Governance Action as stipulated in Article 2, Section 6 (Governance Action Standards) of the Cardano Constitution and is presented via an immutable off-chain document (IPFS). Therefore, we determine that this proposal does not present any clear constitutional violations.",
    "precedentDiscussion": "None",
    "counterargumentDiscussion": "None",
    "conclusion": "For the reasons stated above, we determine that it is constitutional.",
